object.customQuery:
select distinct 
    p.policysystemid, 
    p.policykey, 
    p.policynumber, 
    p.policyversion, 
    p.newbusinesstransactiondt, 
    p.statuscd, 
    p.automaticrenewal, 
    p.customernumber, 
    p.nonrenewalreasons, 
    p.policyeffectivedt, 
    p.policyexpirationdt, 
    p.policyinceptiondt, 
    p.lineofbusiness, 
    p.groupline, 
    p.newrenewalcd, 
    p.carriercd, 
    p.cancelreason, 
    p.insurancescore,  
    p.programcd, 
    p.tier, 
    p.payplancd, 
    p.operator, 
    p.inexperiencedoperator, 
    p.risktypecd, 
    p.sourcecd, 
    p.policyform, 
    p.controllingstatecd, 
    p.shellpolicyind, 
    p.ismigrated, 
    p.fullpolicykey, 
    p.insurancescorerundate, 
    p.insurancescorerunyear, 
    p.secondaryinsurancescore, 
    p.secondaryinsurancescorerundate, 
    p.secondaryinsurancescorerunyear, 
    s.insuredname, 
    s.insuredaddress1, 
    s.insuredaddress2, 
    s.insuredcity, 
    s.insuredzip, 
    s.insuredbirthdt, 
    s.formattedinsuredaddress, 
    i.displayvalue as "insurance score desc", 
    a.agencycd, 
    a.producername, 
    a.paymentpreferencecd,
    a.agentcd,
    r.occupancycd, 
    acd.billingtype, 
    i2.displayvalue 
from dbo.policydetail p  
inner join dbo.insureddetail s on s.policykey = p.policykey
left join dbo.view_dim_insuracescore i on p.insurancescore between i.low and i.hi
left join dbo.view_dim_insuracescore i2 on p.secondaryinsurancescore between i2.low and i2.hi
left join dbo.msgr_palias_agents_vp a on p.providernumber = a.agentcd 
left join dbo.msgr_ralias_risk_vp r on p.policykey = r.policykey and p.policysystemid = r.risksystemid 
left join dbo.msgr_acdalias_accountdetail_vp acd on acd.policykey = p.policynumber + p.policyversion
where s.roweffenddt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
